data.description: This two-story 1584 square foot cabin in the woods features a wraparound porch for nature views at every angle.  Inside you'll find a spacious open living area and kitchen with loads of cabinetry and counterspace.  Large laundry room (washer and dryer to stay) and pantry shelf wall. Main bedroom and bath finish out the first floor. Upstairs you will find the bonus room, second bath, and office/guest room.  Outside you'll find an oversized carport and workshop with electric and plumbing. All this on 3.46 acres with a wet weather creek along the back border of the property. Priced at $299,000.
